  	<a href="https://instagram.com/traintrackapp" rel="publisher" class="mr-2"><i class="fab fa-instagram"></i> Instagram</a>
  	<a href="https://flickr.com/traintrackapp" rel="publisher" class="mr-2"><i class="fab fa-flickr"></i> Flickr</a>
  	<a href="https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCzJtSpuoCxCXkLc2suWwvSw" rel="publisher" class="mr-2"><i class="fab fa-youtube"></i> YouTube</a>
  </p>

</div>
